
NEW IN VERSION 4.0
------------------
- Initial release


NEW IN VERSION 4.1
------------------
- Fixes for Qt 4.2 and 4.3.
- Fixes to enable compilation on Windows.
- TIFF and PDF export.
- New translations (ukrainian)


NEW IN VERSION 4.2
------------------
- Better support of Qt/Mac
- Recent files menu
- Open Location
- Undo/Redo
- Escape can be used to exit full screen mode
